*(200 words max)*

Revive has no analytics, no tracking code, no network calls other than tel:// URLs for emergency dialling, and no third-party dependencies. Every medical protocol was cross-referenced against published guidelines from the American Heart Association, World Health Organization, and wilderness medicine literature.

I built this app because I come from a community that has lived through disasters. Keralites don't wait for help. We organise fishing boats, open our homes, and cook for strangers. Revive is that same instinct turned into code. It's the knowledge I wish every phone had carried during the floods and landslides. Not a replacement for real rescue, but something better than a screen that says "No Service."

